Cara Sniffing Live TV di Chrome
1. instal Chrome extension "Network Sniffer"
2. buka website live streaming, ex: ( vidio.com, visionplus.id, useetv.com indihome.com, dens.tv )
3. klik tombol "Network Sniffer"
4. cari link dengan extension = ts, m3u, m3u8, mpd atau mp3 dkk
5. salam gretongan
